    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2>Each &quot;Box&quot; in Danglebox magnetically connects to its neighbors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/b13fec4c15997a5fb3a65df455a7f5e6.poster.avif?t=1667437572\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/b13fec4c15997a5fb3a65df455a7f5e6.webm?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/b13fec4c15997a5fb3a65df455a7f5e6.mp4?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boost</h2>With the &quot;Magnetic Boost&quot; feature you have some interesting control over your constructs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/4b0de36aa28bc886634e9c05c61801b0.poster.avif?t=1667437572\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/4b0de36aa28bc886634e9c05c61801b0.webm?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/4b0de36aa28bc886634e9c05c61801b0.mp4?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> reconnect boxes<br></li><li> realign boxes<br></li><li> strengthen the connections while active</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ropes</h2>Ropes are an essential part of Danglebox.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/7524a0e0a5847b75f3f6462e49995747.poster.avif?t=1667437572\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/7524a0e0a5847b75f3f6462e49995747.webm?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/7524a0e0a5847b75f3f6462e49995747.mp4?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> collect resource containers<br></li><li> bind your boxes in place or tow them around<br></li><li> rip boxes off your opponent or topple them over!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trains</h2>Trains will supply you with resources, but will also test the stability of your designs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/a70df725ae8cdfc8b13d69737c49f7b6.poster.avif?t=1667437572\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/a70df725ae8cdfc8b13d69737c49f7b6.webm?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743450/extras/a70df725ae8cdfc8b13d69737c49f7b6.mp4?t=1667437572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fly</h2>Conquer the skies with the help of balloons and thrusters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mission Mode: complete objectives<br></li><li> Free Play Mode: choose your starting position, play for fun or battle the AI for resources</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map Editor</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> create missions and free play maps in the included editor</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3 tiers of each: boxes, ropes and balloons<br></li><li> 3 types of weapons: cannon, rocket launcher, electric zapper<br></li><li> weapons, coolers, thrusters and storages become more powerful when next to each other<br></li><li> manually control a train or automate routes with gates<br></li><li> thrusters can be activated with direction keys, pilot your airship, rocket or spaceship!<br></li><li> temperature system, many things produce waste heat, keep your boxes cool!<br></li><li> water physics, wood boxes float!<br></li><li> variable gravity and friction, there are space maps!</li></ul>",
